TopicTitle: Part not recognized in 'test part x contract'?

Does anyone have an idea what's causing this problem?

Or how I can fix it?

This particular contract indicates that you have to be traveling at a certain speed (280 m/s to 450 m/s) at a certain altitude (30,000m to 36,000m).  The screen shot you shared shows that you are landed, so I can't state whether or not you hit those parameters during flight.  Simply having the part is not enough; you have to meet all the requirements in the contract.
